HANDOVER.md:
  66  
  67: - **Generator:** Single self-contained HTML; required sections (Nav, Hero, Features, Social proof, CTA, Footer); no Lorem; strict iframe sandbox (no `allow-same-origin` + `allow-scripts`); validate `OPENAI_API_KEY`. If generation fails, the Builder shows the API error message; set `OPENAI_API_KEY` in `.env.local` for local dev (see `.env.example`).
  68  - **CI:** One main workflow for PRs to `main`; protected paths = middleware, `src/lib/engine/`, Stripe/billing API routes only. Use `[ALLOW-PROTECTED]` in PR title only when changing those.

